{"tid":876473,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實喺香港買樓根本唔難，係你班人唔識錢搵錢啫","createTime":"2018-10-25T15:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T12:58:52.000Z","uid":150100,"like":11,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"abaae6bf251936ebf610dba42ebe5de1030019f8","tid":876473,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T15:42:43.000Z","msg":"假設你每個月返工淨袋10000<br />\n攞5000出嚟買主客和8串1，一中就基本上翻幾倍，然後再買，又再翻幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好同我講咩唔中點算，得嗰3個揀都揀唔中就死咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後仲有嗰5000就先儲起佢，唔係叫你儲嚟買樓，因為白痴先會儲錢嚟買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲錢係儲嚟投資中資股<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係人都知貿易戰一定係中國贏㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國一贏，啲股價一定爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁到時你再放返出去<br />\n起碼都入手價翻幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再加埋你喺馬會賺返嚟啲錢<br />\n唔好話御半山<br />\n半山都嚟緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以話<br />\n你班廢青日日喺度抱怨話上車難<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上車根本就唔難，月薪15k已經夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難係因為你地唔識錢搵錢啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823081e4befdfad5708e8b875a89ef336ac250f8","tid":876473,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T15:48:08.000Z","msg":"冇人想上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132616d3d469a911ceef34b9ca6d6a0cecc24f0b","tid":876473,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T16:09:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502049936a6a2c17b22469b11791882408e1cd20","tid":876473,"uid":138197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl